<P>
   NY-TALL-SHIPS (New York) _ An estimated 5 million spectators are
expected to throng New York City's shores next week for what may be
the greatest nautical spectacle of all time _ an event drawing well
over 120 tall ships, some 42 warships from the United States and 25
other nations and 50,000 to 70,000 small pleasure craft. By Ralph
Blumenthal.
