<HEADLINE>
FOUNDATION HEALTH SYSTEMS TO CUT BACK MEDICARE COVERAGE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By CHRIS SIEROTY 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
