<HEADLINE>
BORED TV NETWORKS SWITCH OFF BLANKET ELECTION COVERAGE  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary, Political Editors)   (This 425-word ``separate-buy'' article is from THE INDEPENDENT
newspaper in London.)  
