December 1999. It suggests some of the high points in this year's
fiction, poetry, nonfiction, mysteries and science fiction. The
books are arranged alphabetically under genre headings. For
complete reviews of these books, check out The New York Times' Web
site, www.nytimes.com/books. &QL;
