<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-30 06:34 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9220 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k BC-CAMPAIGN-TRAIL-MIX-EC     06-30 0411
