   The younger Balon didn't rule out voting for Fox.
</P>
<P>
   (EDs: Begin optional trim.)
</P>
<P>
   Antonia Ramirez of Anenecuilco _ where Zapata was born _ said
she's for Fox and her sister for Labastida. .
</P>
<P>
   ``Fox wants to help people who have to go to the United States
to work,'' said Ramirez, who usually is in Denver working as a
hotel maid. ``But my sister works at Social Security (Mexico's
