   CHICKEN-ADS _ Try an unlikely place - Chick-fil-A.
</P>
<P>
   The restaurant chain has fired off a letter to fast-food rival
Burger King asking it to stop using a promotion for the hit movie
'Chicken Run.'' Chick-fil-A claims spots in the promtion closely
immitate the theme for the popular cow campaign.''The cows were the
ones who told us about it, but they didn't have a lawyer in the
stable,'' said spokesman Don Perry. (Poole, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
