   THOMPSON-COLUMN &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Call me crazy, but I'm gonna miss Elian Gonzalez. The
kid was good for two or three columns a month _ and more than that
when his Miami relatives went on one of their goofy rampages. By
BILL THOMPSON. Story has moved in ``k'' commentary category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
