   IRELAND-MARCHING (Portadown, Northern Ireland) _ This year's
``marching season'' is shaping up to be particularly violent, with
the return of characters such as Protestant firebrand Johnny ``Mad
Dog'' Adair. By Kevin Cullen. 1350 words.
</P>
