   MENINGITIS-STUDENTS (Undated) _ With bacterial meningitis on the
rise among college freshmen, the Centers for Disease Control is
recommending for the first time that all incoming students consider
vaccination against the potentially lethal brain infection. By
Megan Scott. 900 words.
</P>
<P>
   COURT-RAPE (Boston) _ In a decision women's activists say will
cause rape victims to choose between privacy and prosecution,
Massachusetts' highest court has held a rape crisis center in
contempt for refusing to turn over telephone hotline records sought
by lawyers for an accused rapist. By Sacha Pfeiffer. 900 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
