financially troubled Toysmart.com is selling its customer
information in potential violation of the company's own privacy
policies. By Alex Pham. 1000 words.
</P>
<P>
   LYCOS-TERRA (Undated) _ German publishing giant Bertelsmann has
only committed to about a third of the $1 billion it said it would
put into the Lycos-Terra combination, an SEC filing suggests. By
Ross Kerber. 700 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; SPORTS (s) &LR;
</P>
