George Heaven, a 47-year-old engineer, is wound up about his Rubber
Bandit, which he has been working on at the Van Nuys Airport for
the better part of six years. Now, he says, it's ready to fly. By
Brent Hopkins. (Will move in the ``a'' national and ``n''
California state news files.)
