<SLUG> BC-SPEEDWAY0701-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Bush turns around and OKs $2 million for Daytona Speedway
 &HT;    By S.V. Date
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
