<P>
   INVEST-INSIGHT-Q&AMP;A (Undated) _ Time flies when you're having
fun. Zip-zap, and suddenly the year is halfway over. Trouble is,
for most investors the last six months have not been a lot of
laughs. Byron R. Wien, chief U.S. investment strategist for Morgan
Stanley Dean Witter, took some time last week to revisit the recent
past and to talk about the next six months. By Kenneth N. Gilpin.
