<HEADER>
A0253 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v BC-ELIMINATE-RECAP-NYT &LR;      06-30 0035
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-RECAP-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   ALL BUDGETED STORIES HAVE MOVED except:
</P>
<P>
   PRESBYTERIANS-SAMESEX-UNIONS, BBN-RHODEN-COLUMN, BBN-METS-BRAVES
and BBA-YANKS-DEVILRAYS.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y. Times News Service.
</P>
</TEXT>
