RENAULT -- Louis Schweitzer, chairman of Renault, in his Paris
office with a model of the Koleos, a concept car. Schweitzer is
trying to make the company a global auto power through acquisitions
and an internal reorganization. (John Giannini/The New York Times)
</P>
