   LEBANON_Addaiseh map -- 1 x 2 1/4 -- LEBANON-ISRAEL
</P>
<P>
   TURKEY_Belkis map -- 1 x 2 1/4 -- TURKEY-ARCHEO
</P>
<P>
   MEXICO_Border map -- 1 x 2 1/4 -- MEXICO-U.S.-BORDER
</P>
